      <guid>https://fairchild26.github.io/en/cpp/for_each/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;for_each()&lt;/code&gt; is a traversal algorithm that executes a given callable object (functor, lambda expression, function pointer) on each element within a specified range and returns that callable object to obtain its final state.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
